            <p><strong><a href="http://www.socialmediaexaminer.com/facebook-page-layout-changes-how-marketers-should-respond/" target="_blank">Facebook Page Layout Changes: How Marketers Should Respond</a></strong></p>
            <p>Facebook has recently launched a variety of new features for the layouts of Facebook pages. One of the biggest differences is the organization of a Facebook page’s timeline, with various sections displayed more prominently based on the order of a page’s left sidebar tab that links to a page’s unique content, such as Videos, Photos, and Posts. This article breaks down how to make changes to your Facebook page and offers strategies for taking advantage of Facebook’s latest changes.</p>
