            <p><strong><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/15/technology/facebook-fake-news.html" target="_blank">Facebook Mounts Effort to Limit Tide of Fake News</a></strong></p>
            <p>Facebook has long regarded itself as a neutral online space where people can post, read, and share content, regardless of accuracy. In light of growing concerns about the spread of fake news, Facebook recently announced it has mounted a concerted effort to address the issue, which includes initiating a series of experiments it hopes will limit the spread of misinformation on the social network.</p>
